@model PagedList.IPagedList<Apphr.Application.Ortopedia.HojaGasto.DTOs.HojaGastoDTOIxGrid>
@using PagedList.Mvc
<!--Tabla-->
<div class="table-responsive">
    <table id="myTable" class="table table-striped table-bordered display responsive nowrap" width="100%">
        <thead class="table-dark">
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 90px;">Acciones</th>
                <th class="text-center">Fecha</th>
                <th>Número</th>
                <th>Fecha</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            @if (Model != null && Model.Any())
            {
                foreach (var item in Model)
                {
                    <tr>
                        <!-- Acciones -->
                        <td class="text-center">
                            @*<a class="btn btn-sm btn-info" href="@Url.Action("Details", new { id = item.MaterialId })"><i class="far fa-eye"></i></a>*@
                            <div class="dropdown d-inline-block">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button" id="ddBtn" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                    <i class="fas fa-ellipsis-v"></i>
                                </button>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="ddBtn">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" data-model-id="@item.HojaGastoId" onclick="entity.view(this);"><i class="far fa-eye"></i> Ver</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" data-model-id="@item.HojaGastoId" data-action="@Url.Action("CEdit", new { id = item.HojaGastoId, mode = "UPD" })" onclick="entity.update(this);"><i class="fas fa-edit"></i> Editar</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" data-model-id="@item.HojaGastoId" data-model-hoja-gasto="@item.HojaControlSala" onclick="entity.delete(this);"><i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Eliminar</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                        <!-- Acciones -->
                        <td class="text-center">@item.Fecha.ToString("dd/MM/yyyy")</td>
                        <td>@item.HojaControlSala</td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
 }
            }
            else
            { 
                <!--Sin registros-->
                <tr>
                    <td class="text-center" colspan="4">@Apphr.Resources.Strings.NoRegister</td>
                </tr>
                <!--Sin registros-->
            }
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
<!--Tabla-->